** Special Requirements: **

Applicants are required to be Australian Citizens and hold a current
restorable NV1 Defence Security Clearance or be eligible to gain this.
Employment may be contingent on the satisfactory result of criminal and/or
other background screens, which require the collection and transfer of
personal information.

